author: AceShowbiz.com
title: JWoww Announces Second Pregnancy at Wedding to Roger Mathews
text:
Comments The former 'Jersey Shore' star told guests at her wedding on Sunday, October 18 that she's expecting her second child. 
Jenni " JWoww " Farley is now pregnant with her second child, ET Online has learned. A source told the news outlet that the TV personality star first shared the big news with those attending her wedding to Roger Mathews on Sunday, October 18. No other details regarding the baby, including the sex and due date, have been revealed. JWoww and Mathews' new bundle of joy will join their daughter Meilani Alexandra Mathews, who was born on July 13 last year. JWoww and her longtime partner Mathews got engaged in 2012, after he popped the question with a massive 5-carat pink and white rock during a skydiving session. They finally tied the knot over the weekend at Addison Park in Keyport, New Jersey. "I feel so fortunate to have married my best friend!" JWoww said of her big day to In Touch . Among the guests at the wedding were her former " Jersey Shore " co-stars like Nicole " Snooki " Polizzi, Sammi Giancola and Deena Cortese who all also served as her bridesmaids. Vinny Guadagnino, Paul DelVecchio and Ronnie Ortiz-Magro were also in attendance.
